review_text:
What I have learned from reading reviews of _The Intruder_ is people seem to be mad that it wasn't racist enough...

Oh the movie itself? Yeah it was okay.

_Final rating:★★½ - Had a lot that appealed to me, didn’t quite work as a whole._
